* WRITE: Describe the relationship between slope of a linear function and increasing/decreasing.
* ANALYZE: Determine if a graph with more than one x-intercept must be nonlinear.
* PERSEVERE: Deborah fills a tub — maximum 50 gallons at 10 minutes, then decreases to 0 at 30 minutes.
